The SSIS Package Upgrade Wizard upgrades packages created using previous versions of SQL Server tools and object models to SQL Server 2012. The wizard guides you through the steps to upgrade packages stored in SQL Server, the file system, or the SSIS package store.

If you want to analyze your existing packages to obtain a detailed report of potential issues prior to upgrading the packages, install and run the Upgrade Advisor from the SQL Server 2012 distribution media.
